'''金牛座KEPD 350'''{{Efn | Target Adaptive Unitary and Dispenser Robotic Ubiquity System/Kinetic Energy Penetrator and Destroyer.}}是德国和瑞典合作的空射[[巡航导弹|巡航导弹]]，由金牛座公司生产。其用户有德国和[[西班牙|西班牙]]、南韓。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flugrevue.de/militaerluftfahrt/kampfflugzeuge-helikopter/erste-taurus-an-suedkorea-uebergeben/703582|title=Abstandslenkflugkörpersystem: Erste Taurus an Südkorea übergeben|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-21|archive-date=2017-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913232341/http://www.flugrevue.de/militaerluftfahrt/kampfflugzeuge-helikopter/erste-taurus-an-suedkorea-uebergeben/703582|dead-url=no}}</ref>金牛座公司是{{tsl|en|MBDA}}和[[萨博博福斯动力|萨博博福斯动力]]的合資公司。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gripen Multi-Role Fighter Aircraft, Sweden|url=http://www.airforce-technology.com/projects/gripen/|accessdate=2007-07-17|author=|date=|format=|work=www.airforce-technology.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2007-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713033536/http://www.airforce-technology.com/projects/gripen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 概况 ==
金牛座KEPD 350飛彈採用匿蹤技術，射程超過500公里（300英里）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kepd 350|url=http://www.taurus-systems.de/html/kepd350.html|accessdate=September 3, 2007|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Taurus systems|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927180433/http://www.taurus-systems.de/html/kepd350.html|archivedate=2007-09-27|place=DE}}</ref>該彈由[[渦輪扇發動機|渦輪扇發動機]]提供動力，最高飛行速度達到1馬赫。KEPD 350可掛載於[[龍捲風戰機|龍捲風戰機]]、[[F/A-18黃蜂式戰鬥攻擊機|F/A-18]]、[[F-15E打擊鷹式戰鬥轟炸機#F-15K_猛擊鷹|F-15K、]][[JAS_39獅鷲戰鬥機|JAS 39]]與[[颱風戰鬥機|颱風戰鬥機]]等戰機上。

該彈具有兩枚被稱為Mephisto（'''M'''ulti-'''E'''ffect '''P'''enetrator '''HI'''ghly '''S'''ophisticated and '''T'''arget '''O'''ptimised，多效應高精度穿透器 - 目標優化）的500公斤（1,100磅）彈頭，具有預裝藥和[[串联炸药|串聯裝藥]]以清除目標上方的土壤或穿透加固掩體，再使用可變延遲引信控制主彈頭的爆炸。該彈重約1,400公斤（3,100磅），直徑為1公尺（3.3英尺）。金牛座KEPD 350飛彈主要的目標是加固碉堡、機場、港口、橋樑、彈藥庫與指揮、控制、通訊設施。該彈也可攻擊港內或海上航行的船隻。該飛彈也具有多種反反制手段以避免被敵方防禦系統攔截。<ref name="auto" />

任務計劃人員可設定飛彈的飛行路線，該彈將會使用影像導引、[[惯性导航系统|慣性導航系統]]、地形比對系統與[[全球定位系統|全球定位系統]]進行貼地飛行。若飛彈在飛行過程中無法接收到GPS訊號，也可利用內部的導航系統飛行到目標附近。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kepd 350|url=http://www.defense-update.com/products/k/KEPD350.htm|accessdate=2008-05-06|author=|date=|format=|work=Defence Update|publisher=|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302193449/http://www.defense-update.com/products/k/KEPD350.htm|archive-date=2012-03-02}}</ref>一旦到達目標附近，飛彈便開始爬升，以達到可獲取目標影像和最佳攻擊角度的高度。飛彈將會用內建的[[热成像仪|熱成像儀]]辨識目標，並進行攻擊。若沒有發現目標，飛彈將會沿著設定好的飛行路線飛至預設的墜毀地點，以免攻擊錯誤目標或造成不必要的損害。<ref name="Hoyle, Craig 2010">Hoyle, Craig. [https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/germany-receives-last-taurus-cruise-missile-350922/ "Germany receives last Taurus cruise missile"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/germany-receives-last-taurus-cruise-missile-350922/ |date=20161220154754 }} ''Flight global'', 2010-12-14.</ref>

=== 外銷 ===
西班牙空軍購買了45枚金牛座KEPD 350飛彈。金牛座公司成功的將該飛彈整合至西班牙空軍的[[F/A-18黃蜂式戰鬥攻擊機|F/A-18]]上，並在2009年5月於南非進行試射後通過戰術測評。<ref>{{Cite web|title=El Ejército del Aire incrementa su capacidad operativa con la integración del misil Taurus en el F-18|url=http://www.ejercitodelaire.mde.es/ea/pag?idDoc=45DC0A9DED8AD579C12575C4005016F0|accessdate=2009-06-15|author=|date=|format=|work=Ejercito del aire|publisher=MDE|language=es|place=[[Spain|ES]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091223180611/http://www.ejercitodelaire.mde.es/ea/pag?idDoc=45DC0A9DED8AD579C12575C4005016F0|archive-date=2009-12-23}}</ref>

在美國拒絕出售[[AGM-158联合空面导弹|AGM-158]]後，韓國轉而向金牛座公司訂購200枚飛彈以增強[[F-15E打擊鷹式戰鬥轟炸機#F-15K_猛擊鷹|F-15K]]的對地打擊能力。<ref>{{cite web|title=S. Korea to buy bunker busting missiles from Europe|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/04/korea-defense-missiles-idUSL3N0CR1D120130404|accessdate=2013-04-07|author=|date=2013-04-04|format=|publisher=Reuters|language=|archive-date=2013-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130704011637/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/04/korea-defense-missiles-idUSL3N0CR1D120130404|dead-url=no}}</ref>韓國國防採購計劃署（DAPA）於2013年11月簽署了購買合約。根據合約，金牛座公司將在首爾開設辦事處，以處理採購的相關業務與技術轉移。同時，雙方也將合作開發新型巡弋飛彈。該辦公室是金牛座公司在德國以外的第一個辦事處，而KEPD 350是首個整合到韓國戰機上的歐洲飛彈。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2014/05/116_156960.html|title=Taurus Systems to open Seoul office this week|newspaper=The Korea Times|date=2014-05-11|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2014-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140515003523/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2014/05/116_156960.html|dead-url=no}}.</ref>韓國於2016年10月宣布將追加購買90枚金牛座導彈，以應對北韓的威脅。<ref>[http://www.airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/october/2961-south-korea-plans-to-buy-more-taurus-missiles-after-north-korea-s-new-nuclear-test.html South Korea plans to buy more Taurus missiles after North Korea's new nuclear test] {{Wayback|url=http://www.airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/october/2961-south-korea-plans-to-buy-more-taurus-missiles-after-north-korea-s-new-nuclear-test.html |date=20200724123502 }} - Airrecognition.com, 2016-10-04</ref>該批飛彈於2016年12月12日交付<ref>[http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3144-first-batch-of-40-taurus-kepd-350k-cruise-missiles-arrived-in-south-korea.html First batch of 40 Taurus KEPD 350K cruise missiles arrived in South Korea] {{Wayback|url=http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3144-first-batch-of-40-taurus-kepd-350k-cruise-missiles-arrived-in-south-korea.html |date=20200724180652 }} - Airrecognition.com, 2016-12-13</ref>，並於2016年12月22日開始服役。<ref>[http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3177-south-korea-starts-deploying-taurus-cruise-missile-for-combat-use.html South Korea starts deploying Taurus cruise missile for combat use] {{Wayback|url=http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3177-south-korea-starts-deploying-taurus-cruise-missile-for-combat-use.html |date=20200724174902 }} - Airrecognition.com, 2016-12-22</ref>

=== 子型號 ===
[[韓國空軍|韓國空軍]]裝備的KEPD 350K是由KEPD 350升級而來的。該彈安裝了[[罗克韦尔柯林斯|羅克韋爾柯林斯]]公司生產的軍規GPS接收模組，具有選擇性可用性防欺騙模塊（SAASM），可防止電磁干擾。<ref>{{cite web|title=South Korea begins receiving Taurus cruise missiles|url=http://www.janes.com/article/64626/south-korea-begins-receiving-taurus-cruise-missiles|accessdate=|author=|date=14 October 2016|format=|publisher=|language=|last1=Jennings|first1=Gareth|website=[[詹氏資訊集團|詹氏資訊集團]]|access-date=13 December 2016|archive-date=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910111921/http://www.janes.com/article/64626/south-korea-begins-receiving-taurus-cruise-missiles|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年10月，金牛座公司公布了一款名為KEPD 350K-2的飛彈研發計畫。該彈的彈體較小，主要用於輕型戰鬥機如[[FA-50战斗攻击机|FA-50]]。KEPD 350K-2的射程將減少至400公里（250英里），巡航速度為0.6-0.9馬赫。<ref>[http://www.airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-news-2015/october/2056-south-korea-plans-to-arm-its-fa-50-light-combat-fighters-with-new-variant-of-the-taurus-missile.html South Korea plans to arm its FA-50 light combat fighters with new variant of the Taurus missile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-news-2015/october/2056-south-korea-plans-to-arm-its-fa-50-light-combat-fighters-with-new-variant-of-the-taurus-missile.html |date=20151208074223 }} - Airrecognition.com, 2015-10-23</ref>

2016年12月，韓國國防採購計劃署透露，韓國將於2018年開始研發以金牛座KEPD 350為藍本的遠程空對地飛彈。此種新型飛彈預計將由研發中的[[KF-X战斗机|KF-X]]掛載。<ref>[http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3148-south-korea-plans-to-develop-taurus-based-air-to-ground-missile.html South Korea plans to develop Taurus-based air-to-ground missile] {{Wayback|url=http://airrecognition.com/index.php/archive-world-worldwide-news-air-force-aviation-aerospace-air-military-defence-industry/global-defense-security-news/global-news-2016/december/3148-south-korea-plans-to-develop-taurus-based-air-to-ground-missile.html |date=20161220110628 }} - Airrecognition.com, 2016-12-14</ref>

